Titolo: The Pandora Directive

Anno: 1996

Descrizione: The Pandora Directive is the fourth installment in the Tex Murphy series of graphic adventure games produced by Access Software. After its creators reacquired the rights to the series, it was re-released on Good Old Games on July 2, 2009.It was re-released in 2009 on GOG.com for Windows and in 2012 for macOS, and then released on Steam in 2014 with support for Windows, macOS, and Linux. In 2021 Big Finish Games announced that a remaster of The Pandora Directive is in development.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
